# Project Structure

ElysianVista is a full-stack TypeScript monorepo with shared types, using Bun, Hono, Vite, React, and Supabase.

## Main Components

- **Client**: React frontend using Vite, Tailwind, and ShadCN UI components
  - Entry: [client/src/main.tsx](mdc:client/src/main.tsx)
  - Main App: [client/src/App.tsx](mdc:client/src/App.tsx)
  - Components: [client/src/components](mdc:client/src/components)
  - Pages: [client/src/pages](mdc:client/src/pages)

- **Server**: Hono backend API 
  - Entry: [server/src/index.ts](mdc:server/src/index.ts)
  - Middleware: [server/src/middleware.ts](mdc:server/src/middleware.ts)
  - Services: [server/src/services](mdc:server/src/services)

- **Shared**: Types and configurations shared between client and server
  - Main types: [shared/src/types.ts](mdc:shared/src/types.ts)
  - Supabase types: [shared/src/supabase](mdc:shared/src/supabase)
  - Config: [shared/src/config.ts](mdc:shared/src/config.ts)

- **Supabase**: Database seeding and schema
  - Root: [supabase](mdc:supabase)
